### Members API 测试文件
### 使用 VS Code REST Client 或 JetBrains HTTP Client

@baseUrl = http://localhost:5000
@memberId = {{$guid}}

### 注册新会员
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/members
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "张三",
  "phone": "13800138000",
  "email": "zhangsan@example.com"
}

### 查询会员信息
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/members/{{memberId}}

### 充值余额
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/members/{{memberId}}/topup-balance
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "amount": 100.00
}

### 扣减余额
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/members/{{memberId}}/deduct-balance
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "amount": 20.00
}

### 赠送积分
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/members/{{memberId}}/award-points
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "points": 50
}
